Revert "FXML is working with some example code."
This reverts commit 360ef9df

task.summary: Added a new window and played with some stage and scene options.
FXML gridpane layout - parts section main page
Added XML for add part screen. Made exit button work.
Added the rest of the FXML layouts and created controller files.
Add part and modify part buttons are functional
Add and modify product windows are now displaying All cancel buttons work Added toggle groups for radio buttons in add/modify part All windows display as APPLICATION_MODAL
Add Part and Modify Part radio buttons are toggling the machineID/Company Name label text
variable declarations, setters, and getters for Part.java
Parts can be added, and are being displayed in the tableView!!!
Some fields are now being populated when modify parts is opened.
Value is now displayed in the disabled ID fields in add part and modify part
modify part screen save function is working
Add and modify part windows now close when saving
